'''2013年新加坡小印度骚乱'''（{{lang-en|'''2013 Little India riot'''}}；{{lang-ta|'''2013 லிட்டில் இந்தியா கலவரம்'''}}）是於2013年12月8日发生在[[新加坡|新加坡]][[小印度_(新加坡)|小印度]]的[[暴乱|暴乱]]。

起因为於[[新加坡標準時間|新加坡时间]]晚上21:23分，一名[[印度|印度]]客工在[[小印度|小印度]]跑马埔路（{{lang|en|Race Course Rd}}）和翰莎路（{{lang|en|Hampshire Rd}}）的十字路口被一辆私人巴士撞倒后当场丧命，引发工友及路人不满，聚众包围袭击了肇事车辆、[[警察车|警察车]]及随后赶到的[[救护车|救护车]]。逾300名外籍客工参与此事，暴乱共持续兩个多小时。<ref name="st-300"/>这起事件是[[新加坡独立|新加坡独立]]后的第二起暴乱，自[[1969年新加坡種族暴動|1969年种族暴动]]后40余年内的首宗暴乱。<ref name=bbcnews>{{cite news|last=Nghiem|first=Ashleigh|title=Singapore bus death triggers riot|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25294918|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=BBC News|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213105238/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25294918|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=australian-newspaper>{{cite news|title=Rare riot shuts down Singapore's Little India district|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/rare-riot-shuts-down-singapores-little-india-district/story-e6frg6so-1226778385511|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=[[The_Australian|The Australian]]|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2014-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507100854/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/rare-riot-shuts-down-singapores-little-india-district/story-e6frg6so-1226778385511|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cnn>{{cite news|last=Brown|first=Sophie|title=Dozens arrested in Singapore after foreign worker's death sparks riot|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/12/09/world/asia/singapore-little-india-riot/index.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_latest+%28RSS%3A+Most+Recent%29|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=CNN|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207145912/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/12/09/world/asia/singapore-little-india-riot/index.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_latest+%28RSS%3A+Most+Recent%29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==暴乱过程==
暴乱持续逾两小时，直至午夜时分暴乱地区的局势才得以控制，<ref name="todayonline1">{{cite web |last=Chin |first=Neo Chai |url=http://www.todayonline.com/singapore/riot-breaks-out-little-india |title=Riot breaks out at Little India |publisher=Today |date=2013-12-09 |accessdate=2013-12-08 |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210215432/http://www.todayonline.com/singapore/riot-breaks-out-little-india |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[新加坡警察部队|新加坡警察部队]]特别行动指挥处和辜加警察团都参与其中。<ref name="todayonline1"/>一位目击者报告，一些暴徒呈现醉酒状态，并且向警務和民防部隊人員投掷石块、酒瓶及垃圾桶。<ref name=standardhk-a>{{cite news|title=Migrant labor activists suspect pent-up rage exploded in Singapore riot|url=http://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking_news_detail.asp?id=44133&icid=1&d_str=|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=The Standard (Hong Kong)|date=2013-12-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213124242/http://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking_news_detail.asp?id=44133&icid=1&d_str=|archivedate=2013-12-13}}</ref> 滋事者还将警察车和救护车推翻，并且纵火烧车，导致一辆救护车被烧后引发[[爆炸|爆炸]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zaobao.com/news/singapore/story20131210-286263|title=小印度暴乱事件簿|publisher=联合早报|author=杨萌、苏文琪、张嫥芯|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131210015841/http://www.zaobao.com/news/singapore/story20131210-286263|archivedate=2013-12-10|accessdate=2013-12-10}}</ref>

[[新加坡警察部隊|新加坡警察部隊]]出动[[防暴车|防暴车]]，並且派遣约300員警察力量参与平定事件，<ref name=cnn />12月8日11时许逐步控制了局面，在现场逮捕数十人。12月9日凌晨，所有滋事者被驱离现场。<ref>{{cite web |author=Chan, Francis |url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2013/12/08/Singapore-riots-little-india.aspx |title=Rioting in Singapore's Little India, busloads of riot police dispatched |publisher=The Star Online |date=2013-12-08 |accessdate=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208181142/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2013/12/08/Singapore-riots-little-india.aspx |archive-date=2013-12-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

