==事件后续==
[[File:Mercedes-Benz_ambulance_damaged_during_the_2013_Little_India_riots,_Singapore_-_20131209.jpg|thumbnail]]
25辆救护车被暴徒及滋事者毁坏，其中5辆被烧毁。<ref name=yahoonews>{{cite news|title=Deceased foreign worker in Little India Riot was drunk: Police|url=http://sg.news.yahoo.com/fire--rioting-taking-place-in-little-india--reports-152651999.html|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2013-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210024245/http://sg.news.yahoo.com/fire--rioting-taking-place-in-little-india--reports-152651999.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>上传网络的现场影片画面显示，暴徒将停靠在他们一侧的警车掀翻并且纵火燃烧一辆救护车。<ref name=cnn /><ref name="todayonline1"/>39名警察、4名新加坡民防部队成员和一些辅警受伤。<ref name=yahoonews />

一共有约400名客工参与骚乱。<ref name=bbcnews/><ref name=ft-8dec>{{cite news|last=Grant|first=Jeremy|title=Riot tarnishes Singapore's image as place of ethnic harmony|url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/9266db8a-602e-11e3-b360-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2msn9OzlE|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]]|date=2013-12-08|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911231442/https://www.ft.com/content/9266db8a-602e-11e3-b360-00144feabdc0#axzz2msn9OzlE|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[新加坡警察部队|新加坡警察部队]]出动300名暴动警察。<ref name=bbcnews/>12月9日，新加坡警方召开了记者会，通报事件进展，新加坡副总理兼内政部长[[张志贤|张志贤]]出席。警方称已逮捕27名涉嫌暴动或是暴乱后不肯离去的人员，这些人均来自南亚国家，其中24人为印度国籍、两人为孟加拉国国籍还有一人为新加坡永久居民<ref>{{cite news|title=Little India Riot: 27 suspects from South Asia arrested in connection with the riot|newspaper=The Straits Times|authors=Walter Sim, Joyce Lim & Kash Cheong|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/singapore/story/27-suspects-south-asia-arrested-connection-the-little-india-riot-2013|date=2013-12-09|accessdate=2013-12-09}}</ref><ref name=asiaone-27charged>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/singapore/story/little-india-riot-spore-pr-among-27-arrested-police-20131209 |title=Little India Riot: S'pore PR among 27 arrested: police |publisher=Straits Times |date=2013-12-09 |accessdate=2013-12-09}}</ref>。经进一步调查后，证实两名孟加拉籍客工和一名新加坡永久居民没有参与骚乱事件。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-12-10/an-singapore-to-charge-24-people-for-rioting/5147754 |title=Singapore to charge 24 people for rioting – Australia Network News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation) |publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210101138/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-12-10/an-singapore-to-charge-24-people-for-rioting/5147754 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年12月11日至14日，多9名來自[[泰米爾納德邦|泰米爾納德邦]]的印度籍客工因参与骚乱，而面对相同控状，被控上法庭。3名于11日被控，<ref name=cna-11dec>{{cite news|last=See|first=Sharon|title=3 more charged with rioting at Little India|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/3-more-charged-with/918860.html|publisher=Channel NewsAsia|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2013-12-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214004849/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/3-more-charged-with/918860.html|archivedate=2013-12-14}}</ref>4名于12日被控，<ref name=sti-12dec>{{cite news|last=Singh|first=Khushwant|title=Little India Riot: Four more Indian nationals charged, remanded for further investigations|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/the-big-story/little-india-riot/story/little-india-riot-four-more-indian-nationals-charged-remanded-|publisher=Straits Times|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2013-12-17|archive-date=2013-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215224307/http://www.straitstimes.com/the-big-story/little-india-riot/story/little-india-riot-four-more-indian-nationals-charged-remanded-|dead-url=no}}</ref>两名于14日被控，<ref name=sti-14dec>{{cite news|title=Little India Riot: Two more Indian nationals charged in court|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/singapore/story/little-india-riot-two-more-indian-nationals-charged-court-20131214|publisher=Straits Times|date=2013-12-14|accessdate=2013-12-17|archive-date=2013-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217030858/http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/singapore/story/little-india-riot-two-more-indian-nationals-charged-court-20131214|dead-url=no}}</ref>将被提控人数提高至33名。2014年2月10日，一名印度建築工人因與騷亂有關的指控被判處15週監禁。<ref>{{cite web|title=Indian Man jailed for 15 Weeks on charges of Little India Riots Singapore|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/02/indian-man-jailed-for-15-weeks-on-charges-of-little-india-riots-singapore/|access-date=11 February 2014|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|agency=Indo-Asian News Service|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714083537/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/02/indian-man-jailed-for-15-weeks-on-charges-of-little-india-riots-singapore/|archive-date=14 July 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>2014年10月2日，一名男子因推翻警車被判處25個月監禁，並鞭刊三下。<ref>{{cite web|title=Man who flipped police car in Little India riot gets 25 months' jail and canning|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/courts-crime/man-who-flipped-police-car-in-little-india-riot-gets-25-months-jail-and|access-date=28 April 2020|date=2 October 2014|website=The Straits Times|last1=Chong|first1=Elena|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413013746/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/courts-crime/man-who-flipped-police-car-in-little-india-riot-gets-25-months-jail-and}}</ref>2014年12月2日，一名建築工人因在騷亂中襲擊警察而被判處一年監禁。<ref>{{cite web|title=Little India riot: Foreign worker jailed a year for assaulting a police officer|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/courts-crime/little-india-riot-foreign-worker-jailed-a-year-for-assaulting-a-police|access-date=28 April 2020|date=2 December 2014|website=The Straits Times|last1=Poh|first1=Ian|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413013757/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/courts-crime/little-india-riot-foreign-worker-jailed-a-year-for-assaulting-a-police}}</ref>

此外，有53名工人被驅逐出境，罪名包括妨礙警察行動、不遵守警察命令驅散，<ref>{{cite web|title=Little India Riot: Police hold press conference on repatriation of workers involved in riot|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/little-india-riot-police-hold-press-conference-on-repatriation-of-workers-involved-in-ri-0|access-date=28 April 2020|date=20 December 2013|website=The Straits Times|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413013747/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/little-india-riot-police-hold-press-conference-on-repatriation-of-workers-involved-in-ri-0}}</ref>另外在場的200名工人收到了要求此後遵守法律的政府文件。<ref>{{cite web|title=Little India riot: 200 foreign workers receive police advisories|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/little-india-riot-200-foreign-workers-receive-police-advisories|access-date=28 April 2020|date=22 December 2013|website=The Straits Times|last1=Lee|first1=Pearl|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413013755/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/little-india-riot-200-foreign-workers-receive-police-advisories}}</ref>

這次騷亂最終導致了一項新法律的實施，即2015年的《酒類控制（供應和消費）法》，禁止從晚上10:30到早上 7點在所有公共場所飲酒。 這還包括禁止在這段時間內銷售朗姆酒和葡萄乾冰淇淋等酒精產品，不過這該禁令於 2019年取消。<ref>{{cite web|title=Update on MHA's Review Of Exemption of Food Products Containing Alcohol|url=https://www.mha.gov.sg/newsroom/press-release/news/update-on-mha-review-of-exemption-of-food-products-containing-alcohol|access-date=24 October 2019|date=17 January 2019|website=MHA|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024065410/https://www.mha.gov.sg/newsroom/press-release/news/update-on-mha-review-of-exemption-of-food-products-containing-alcohol|archive-date=24 October 2019|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Food products with alcohol can be sold after 10.30pm as MHA lifts restrictions from Jan 18|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/mha-lifts-liquor-control-act-restrictions-on-food-products-containing-alcohol|access-date=24 October 2019|date=17 January 2019|website=The Straits Times|last1=Goh|first1=Timothy|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413013753/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/mha-lifts-liquor-control-act-restrictions-on-food-products-containing-alcohol}}</ref>

==各方反应==
=== 国内反应 ===
[[新加坡總理|新加坡總理]][[李显龙|李显龙]]下令內政部設立調查委員會徹查騷亂原因，檢討應對現有外籍勞工聚集的措施，以法律为准绳，严惩肇事者。<ref name=aj-9dec />随后他指出这场暴乱是一起孤立事件，呼吁民众不要煽動排外情緒抹黑所有外籍勞工。<ref>{{cite news|title=Singapore riot: PM Lee Hsien Loong urges restraint|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25306425|accessdate=2013-12-09|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2020-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201150336/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25306425|dead-url=no}}</ref> 新加坡副总理兼内政部长张志贤表示，将不遗余力的缉拿漏网的暴徒。<ref name="todayonline1" />副总理张志贤也呼吁民众保持冷静，新加坡警方也将查找其他逃逸的暴徒，严厉和公正地调查案件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zaobao.com/special/report/singapore/littleindiariot/story20131209-285849|title=小印度暴乱记者会汇总|publisher=联合早报|author=苏文琪|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911231410/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/report/singapore/littleindiariot/story20131209-285849|dead-url=no}}</ref>

新加坡交通部长[[吕德耀|吕德耀]]在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上发表文字，表示将考虑在小印度试行限酒措施。12月9日，内政部第二部长[[易华仁|易华仁]]宣布，警方在事件发生的第一个周末对小印度商店实行禁止售卖酒精饮料的临时性措施。

